               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-56rb)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6va)
 I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 6va-9rb)
 I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 9va-10rb)
 I-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām:
                     36 miracles (fols. 10rb-56rb)
 I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi... "Does not the man..."
                     (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 13vb-51va)</summary>
